# Internal security/code audits — kept local only.
# STATUS.md is here too because it summarizes audit findings (open
# CRITICOs/ALTOs with file:line references) which become an exploit
# roadmap in a public repo. SKILLS_AUDIT.md is generated from the local
# environment and reveals which CLIs are installed on the author's box.
# USER_GUIDE.md is intentionally NOT ignored — it's the public manual.
docs/audits/
docs/STATUS.md
docs/SKILLS_AUDIT.md

# Backup of .git/ (local snapshot before risky operations)
.git.backup/

